<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Verifikasi Dokumen — Inspira Mailer</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/Group 1597880519.png">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 32px 16px;
  background: #060f2e; position: relative; overflow-x: hidden;
}
body::before {
  content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 30%, rgba(26,86,168,.55) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 80% 70%, rgba(15,50,112,.6) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 80% at 50% 10%, rgba(7,24,64,.8) 0%, transparent 70%);
  animation: bgShift 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate; z-index: 0;
}
@keyframes bgShift {
  0%   { opacity: 1; }
  50%  { opacity: .85; }
  100% { opacity: 1; }
}
body::after {
  content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0;
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 32px 32px; z-index: 0;
}
.orb { position: fixed; border-radius: 50%; filter: blur(60px); opacity: .25; z-index: 0; animation: floatOrb linear infinite; }
.orb-1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: #1a56a8; top: -100px; left: -100px; animation-duration: 20s; }
.orb-2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: #0f3270; bottom: -80px; right: -80px; animation-duration: 16s; animation-delay: -5s; }
.orb-3 { width: 250px; height: 250px; background: #2e6abf; top: 40%; left: 60%; animation-duration: 24s; animation-delay: -10s; }
@keyframes floatOrb {
  0%,100% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
  25%      { transform: translate(30px, -40px) scale(1.05); }
  50%      { transform: translate(-20px, 30px) scale(.95); }
  75%      { transform: translate(40px, 20px) scale(1.03); }
}

.card {
  position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 100%; max-width: 480px;
  background: #fff; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,.08), 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.2), 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
}

.header-valid {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #071840 0%, #0f3270 55%, #1a56a8 100%);
  padding: 40px 28px 52px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.header-invalid {
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #7f1d1d 55%, #c0392b 100%);
  padding: 40px 28px 52px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.header-valid::before, .header-invalid::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,.08) 0%, transparent 45%);
}
.header-valid::after, .header-invalid::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 36px; background: #fff; border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0 / 100% 100% 0 0;
}
.badge-ring {
  position: relative; z-index: 1; width: 68px; height: 68px; border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 20px;
}
.header-eyebrow { position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.header-title   { position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 6px; }
.header-sub     { position: relative; z-index: 1; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }

.body { padding: 8px 28px 24px; }

.doc-badge {
  background: #f0f5ff; border: 1px solid #c7d9f5; border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0;
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
}
.doc-badge-icon { color: #1a56a8; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
.doc-badge-label { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.doc-badge-value { font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.4; }
.doc-badge-sub   { font-size: 11.5px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 2px; }

.signer {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
  padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.signer-av {
  width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3270, #1a56a8);
  color: #fff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.signer-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.signer-sub  { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }

.info-row {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f7fa;
}
.info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.info-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 5px; }
.dot-amber { background: #f59e0b; }
.dot-blue  { background: #3b82f6; }
.dot-green { background: #22c55e; }
.info-label { font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.info-value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: #111827; line-height: 1.4; }

.scan-badge {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  background: #f0f5ff; border: 1px solid #c7d9f5; border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 10px 14px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #374151;
}
.scan-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #1a56a8; animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite; flex-shrink: 0; }
@keyframes blink { 0%,100% { opacity:1; } 50% { opacity:.2; } }

.stamp {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  background: #f0f5ff; border: 1px solid #bfcfed; border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px;
}
.stamp-icon { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f3270, #1a56a8); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
.stamp-text { font-size: 13px; color: #1e3a6e; line-height: 1.5; }

.invalid-box { margin: 8px 0; background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center; }
.invalid-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: #991b1b; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.invalid-desc  { font-size: 13px; color: #7f1d1d; line-height: 1.6; }

.footer { padding: 14px 28px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #f5f5f5; text-align: center; }
.footer-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.footer-logo { width: 15px; height: 15px; object-fit: contain; opacity: .35; }
.footer-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #9ca3af; }
.footer-note { font-size: 11px; color: #c4c9d4; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="orb orb-1"></div>
<div class="orb orb-2"></div>
<div class="orb orb-3"></div>

<div class="card">

<%
const M   = ['Januari','Februari','Maret','April','Mei','Juni','Juli','Agustus','September','Oktober','November','Desember'];
const p   = n => String(n).padStart(2,'0');
const fdt = dt => `${dt.getDate()} ${M[dt.getMonth()]} ${dt.getFullYear()}, ${p(dt.getHours())}.${p(dt.getMinutes())}.${p(dt.getSeconds())}`;
%>

<% if (valid && signer) {
  const inits = signer.userName.split(' ').slice(0,2).map(w => w[0]).join('').toUpperCase();
  const roleLabels = { admin:'Administrator', direktur:'Direktur', user:'Pengguna' };
  const roleText = signer.userRole ? (roleLabels[signer.userRole] || signer.userRole) : (signer.userOrg || '');
%>

  <div class="header-valid">
    <div class="badge-ring">
      <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none">
        <path d="M7 15l6 6 10-10" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Verifikasi Dokumen Berhasil</div>
    <div class="header-title">Tanda Tangan Sah &amp; Valid</div>
    <div class="header-sub">QR dokumen ini terverifikasi dan dapat dipercaya</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">

    <% if (surat) { %>
    <div class="doc-badge">
      <div class="doc-badge-icon">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M13 2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7l-4-5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M13 2v5h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="doc-badge-label">Dokumen</div>
        <div class="doc-badge-value"><%= surat.perihal %></div>
        <div class="doc-badge-sub">
          Dari: <strong><%= surat.dariInstansi %></strong>
          <% if (surat.nomorSurat) { %> &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; No. <%= surat.nomorSurat %><% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="signer">
      <div class="signer-av"><%= inits %></div>
      <div>
        <div class="signer-name"><%= signer.userName %></div>
        <div class="signer-sub"><%= roleText %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-dot dot-amber"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="info-label">Waktu QR Dibuat</div>
          <div class="info-value"><%= fdt(new Date(signer.addedAt)) %> WIB</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-dot dot-green"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="info-label">Status</div>
          <div class="info-value" style="color:#16a34a;">Tanda Tangan Aktif &amp; Valid</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scan-badge">
      <div class="scan-dot"></div>
      <span>Dipindai pada <%= fdt(scanTime) %> WIB</span>
    </div>

    <div class="stamp">
      <div class="stamp-icon">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
          <path d="M4 10l3.5 3.5 8-8" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="stamp-text">
        Dokumen ini <strong>SAH</strong>. Tanda tangan digital diterbitkan melalui <strong>Inspira Mailer</strong>. Setiap QR unik per dokumen per penandatangan.
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

<% } else { %>

  <div class="header-invalid">
    <div class="badge-ring">
      <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 30 30" fill="none">
        <path d="M8 8l14 14M22 8L8 22" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="header-eyebrow">Verifikasi Gagal</div>
    <div class="header-title">Dokumen Tidak Valid</div>
    <div class="header-sub">QR Code ini tidak dapat diverifikasi</div>
  </div>

  <div class="body">
    <div class="invalid-box">
      <div class="invalid-title">QR Dokumen Tidak Dikenali</div>
      <div class="invalid-desc">
        QR Code ini tidak valid, sudah dihapus, atau telah dimodifikasi.<br>
        Hubungi penerbit dokumen untuk konfirmasi keaslian.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<% } %>

  <div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <img src="/img/Group 1597880519.png" class="footer-logo" alt="">
      <span class="footer-name">Inspira Mailer</span>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-note">QR Dokumen berbeda dari QR Tanda Tangan Pribadi</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
